files

-- base64.h base64.c
   Functions for encoding and decoding scene settings. Encoding is used at the
   client side and decoding is used at the depot.

-- scene_xml2ascii.h scene_xml2ascii.c
   An utility called by lors_compute for parsing the xml scene setting and 
   encoding its content to an ascii string. The ascii string is passed to 
   the intended nfu operation at a remote depot.

-- scene_ascii2val.h scene_ascii2val.c
   Functions for decoding the ascii string to meaningful scene setting values.

-- scene.xsd scene_test.xml
   An example scene setting xml file based on the scene setting schema.
   
-- ascii2val_test.c
   An test program that uses functions defined in scene_ascii2val.h.
